{"tid":1935343,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"王進洋及劉澤鋒曾入紙進行反廿三條遊行 期後取消","createTime":"2020-03-20T13:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T03:13:21.000Z","uid":306337,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d3198c1db1eeaba01b912cb704bc1ff930084a03","tid":1935343,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"轉自 王進洋 facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101197744629082/posts/200684124680443/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101197744629082%2Fposts%2F200684124680443%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=60967211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101197744629082/posts/200684124680443/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【取消大遊行通知】<br />\n<br />\n19 / 3 , 我與前學聯副會長<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">劉澤鋒 Nathan Lau</span></strong>在尖沙咀警署與不同部門代表展開了會議，申請舉辦<span style=\"color: red;\">「反廿三條大遊行」。</span><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫症當前，經舉辦團隊慎重考慮後，為免政治淩駕專業，我們一致決定取消遊行安排；希望香港人團結抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意香港嘅野比人打爛曬，但我介意香港有人死。"},{"pid":"3f2d2a5173669fefbe9344d8c16ffac838d711b4","tid":1935343,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"好能慘 p牌推唔起"},{"pid":"bef32d9b6d28bf043b4610c9581a9594d0f4942d","tid":1935343,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人推"},{"pid":"01ca1aa68c0ba0748e3cd5b6e6ffb37fc1b938a6","tid":1935343,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"推23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9da235c882590a5e9f17106b5ada7975cef337","tid":1935343,"uid":278496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人冇咗香港都會冇埋riphk"},{"pid":"d9df645c197b5b177fc9e7590c435955ffdff30e","tid":1935343,"uid":5158,"